<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="卜官运">卜官运<a href="http://jinzedev.github.io/en/blog/qian-gua#%E5%8D%9C%E5%AE%98%E8%BF%90" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 卜官运" title="Direct link to 卜官运">​</a></h2>
<p>平步青云要<strong>居上位而不骄、往下看</strong>；（官人站在楼梯上，向下看）</p>
<p><strong>要对禄断念；</strong> （空中有鹿，空想，禄要放在空中）</p>
<p><strong>有重立门户之象；</strong>  （有工匠，改门面）</p>
<p><strong>事业还未成功；</strong> （玉在石头中间）</p>
<p><strong>政治清明</strong>，困惑来自自身。（月在当空，清明）</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="卜事">卜事<a href="http://jinzedev.github.io/en/blog/qian-gua#%E5%8D%9C%E4%BA%8B" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 卜事" title="Direct link to 卜事">​</a></h2>
